name: HKWorkoutActivityType
desc: The type of activity performed during a workout.

items.name: case trackAndField
items.desc: Participating in track and field events, including shot put, javelin, pole vaulting, and related sports.

items.name: case americanFootball
items.desc: The constant for playing American football.

items.name: case australianFootball
items.desc: The constant for playing Australian football.

items.name: case discSports
items.desc: The constant for playing disc sports such as Ultimate and Disc Golf.

items.name: case hockey
items.desc: The constant for playing hockey, including ice hockey, field hockey, and related sports.

items.name: case preparationAndRecovery
items.desc: The constant for warm-up and therapeutic activities like foam rolling and stretching.

items.name: case flexibility
items.desc: The constant for a flexibility workout.

items.name: case cooldown
items.desc: The constant for low intensity stretching and mobility exercises following a more vigorous workout.

items.name: case running
items.desc: The constant for running and jogging.

items.name: case wheelchairWalkPace
items.desc: The constant for a wheelchair workout at walking pace.

items.name: case wheelchairRunPace
items.desc: The constant for wheelchair workout at running pace.

items.name: case elliptical
items.desc: The constant for workouts on an elliptical machine.

items.name: case functionalStrengthTraining
items.desc: The constant for strength training, primarily with free weights and body weight.

items.name: case traditionalStrengthTraining
items.desc: The constant for strength training exercises primarily using machines or free weights.

items.name: case crossTraining
items.desc: The constant for exercise that includes any mixture of cardio, strength, and/or flexibility training.

items.name: case mixedCardio
items.desc: The constant for workouts that mix a variety of cardio exercise machines or modalities.

items.name: case highIntensityIntervalTraining
items.desc: The constant for high intensity interval training.

items.name: case stairClimbing
items.desc: The constant for workouts using a stair climbing machine.

items.name: case stairs
items.desc: The constant for running, walking, or other drills using stairs (for example, in a stadium or inside a multilevel building).

items.name: case stepTraining
items.desc: The constant for training using a step bench.

items.name: case fitnessGaming
items.desc: The constant for playing fitness-based video games.

items.name: case cardioDance
items.desc: The constant for cardiovascular dance workouts.

items.name: case socialDance
items.desc: The constant for dancing with a partner or partners, such as swing, salsa, or folk dances.

items.name: case mindAndBody
items.desc: The constant for performing activities like walking meditation, Gyrotonic exercise, and Qigong.

items.name: case pilates
items.desc: The constant for a pilates workout.

items.name: case tableTennis
items.desc: The constant for playing table tennis.

items.name: case equestrianSports
items.desc: The constant for activities that involve riding a horse, including polo, horse racing, and horse riding.

items.name: case play
items.desc: The constant for play-based activities like tag, dodgeball, hopscotch, tetherball, and playing on a jungle gym.

items.name: case crossCountrySkiing
items.desc: The constant for cross country skiing.

items.name: case snowSports
items.desc: The constant for a variety of snow sports, including sledding, snowmobiling, or building a snowman.

items.name: case skatingSports
items.desc: The constant for skating activities, including ice skating, speed skating, inline skating, and skateboarding.

items.name: case paddleSports
items.desc: The constant for canoeing, kayaking, paddling an outrigger, paddling a stand-up paddle board, and related sports.

items.name: case surfingSports
items.desc: The constant for a variety of surf sports, including surfing, kite surfing, and wind surfing.

items.name: case waterFitness
items.desc: The constant for aerobic exercise performed in shallow water.

items.name: case waterPolo
items.desc: The constant for playing water polo.

items.name: case waterSports
items.desc: The constant for a variety of water sports, including water skiing, wake boarding, and related activities.

items.name: case martialArts
items.desc: The constant for practicing martial arts.

items.name: case other
items.desc: The constant for a workout that does not match any of the other workout activity types.
